Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.60,0:43:47.72,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}You save 注意到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.52,0:43:54.61,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}连同我们邂逅的所有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.53,0:44:05.49,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an3}I promise to 飞往那天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.63,0:44:19.36,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}你那无尽的爱语如今尚环绕耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.94,0:44:32.31,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}但现在只能接受命运的无情
